## ūüíé What Makes CodeVista Unique

1. **Zero dependencies** ‚ÄĒ pure Python stdlib, no pip install headaches
2. **Single HTML output** ‚ÄĒ share one file, works offline forever, no server
3. **Deep code smell detection** ‚ÄĒ 19 smell categories with AST-level analysis, not just regex
4. **Architecture pattern detection** ‚ÄĒ identifies 12+ patterns from structure + code
5. **Code age √ó risk correlation** ‚ÄĒ statistical analysis of age, complexity, and churn
6. **Multi-format export** ‚ÄĒ HTML, JSON, Markdown, SARIF, CSV, YAML, PDF
7. **Docker support** ‚ÄĒ multi-stage build, non-root user, PDF-ready
8. **Beautiful design** ‚ÄĒ dark mode, glassmorphism, inline SVG charts, animations
9. **Works on any codebase** ‚ÄĒ 50+ languages, no configuration needed
10. **CI/CD ready** ‚ÄĒ SARIF export for GitHub Code Scanning integration

## ūüŹóÔłŹ Architecture

```
codevista/
‚Ēú‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ cli.py            # CLI interface (argparse)
‚Ēú‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ analyzer.py       # Core analysis engine
‚Ēú‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ report.py         # HTML report generator
‚Ēú‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ metrics.py        # Health scores & recommendations
‚Ēú‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ smells.py         # Code smell detection (19 categories)
‚Ēú‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ architecture.py   # Architecture pattern detector
‚Ēú‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ code_age.py       # Code age & risk analysis
‚Ēú‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ export.py         # Multi-format export (HTML/JSON/MD/SARIF/CSV/YAML/PDF)
‚Ēú‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ security.py       # Secret/vulnerability scanning
‚Ēú‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ dependencies.py   # Dependency parsing & analysis
‚Ēú‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ git_analysis.py   # Git stats extraction
‚Ēú‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ trends.py         # Trend analysis & snapshot tracking
‚Ēú‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ team.py           # Team metrics & collaboration analysis
‚Ēú‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ integrations.py   # CI/CD output (SARIF, Checkstyle, JUnit, GitLab)
‚Ēú‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ decay.py          # Architectural decay detector
‚Ēú‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ codedna.py        # CodeDNA fingerprinter
‚Ēú‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ lint_rules.py     # Language-specific lint rules (PEP 8, Airbnb, gofmt, clippy, Google)
‚Ēú‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ languages.py      # Language definitions & colors
‚Ēú‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ config.py         # Configuration & ignore patterns
‚Ēú‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ utils.py          # Utilities & color schemes
‚ĒĒ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ templates/        # HTML templates
```

## ūüõ†ÔłŹ Tech Stack

- **Python 3.7+** (stdlib only)
- **Inline SVG** for all charts
- **CSS custom properties** for theming
- **Vanilla JavaScript** for interactivity
- **AST parsing** for deep code analysis (Python)

